    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>27 <strong>Def</strong> 度量空间<span class="math inline">\(X\)</span>中一点<span class="math inline">\(p\)</span>是集合<span class="math inline">\(E \subset X\)</span>的<em>聚点(condensation point)</em>, 若每个<span class="math inline">\(p\)</span>的邻域都包含不可数个<span class="math inline">\(E\)</span>中的点. 令<span class="math inline">\(E \subset \mathbb{R}^k\)</span>, <span class="math inline">\(E\)</span>不可数, 令<span class="math inline">\(P\)</span>为<span class="math inline">\(E\)</span>所有聚点的集合. 证明<span class="math inline">\(P\)</span>是完全集且<span class="math inline">\(E \cap P^C\)</span>至多可数.</p><p><em>Proof.</em> 令<span class="math inline">\(V_n\)</span>为<span class="math inline">\(\mathbb{R}^k\)</span>的一个可数基, 令<span class="math inline">\(W\)</span>为使得<span class="math inline">\(E \cap V_n\)</span>至多可数的<span class="math inline">\(V_n\)</span>的并. 下证<span class="math inline">\(P = W^C\)</span>. 若<span class="math inline">\(x \in P\)</span>, 假设<span class="math inline">\(x \in W\)</span>, 则<span class="math inline">\(x \in V_n\)</span>, 且存在<span class="math inline">\(r&gt;0\)</span>使<span class="math inline">\(N_r(x) \subset V_n\)</span>, 由于<span class="math inline">\(E \cap V_n\)</span>至多可数, 有<span class="math inline">\(E \cap N_r(x)\)</span>至多可数, 与<span class="math inline">\(x \in P\)</span>矛盾. 若<span class="math inline">\(x \in W\)</span>, 类似的可以得到<span class="math inline">\(x \in P^C\)</span>. <span class="math inline">\(P = W^C\)</span>得证. <span class="math inline">\(E \cap P^C\)</span>至多可数. 易知<span class="math inline">\(P\)</span>是闭集, 下证<span class="math inline">\(P \in P&#39;\)</span>. 令<span class="math inline">\(x \in P\)</span>, 假设<span class="math inline">\(x \not\in P&#39;\)</span>, 则存在<span class="math inline">\(x\)</span>的一个邻域<span class="math inline">\(O\)</span>, 使得<span class="math inline">\(O \setminus x \subset P^C = W\)</span>. 从而, <span class="math inline">\((O \setminus x)\cap E \subset W \cap E\)</span>. 由<span class="math inline">\(x \in P\)</span>, <span class="math inline">\((O \setminus x)\cap E\)</span>不可数, 而<span class="math inline">\(W \cap E\)</span>可数, 矛盾.</p><p><span class="math display">\[    x&#39;&#39; + x&#39; + x = \sin x\]</span></p><p>Test</p><blockquote><p>Quote</p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    
    
